Greek Finance Minister Evangelos
Venizelos said Greek lawmakers have failed to understand the
risk that the economy grinds to a halt. Speaking in Parliament
today, he said budget cuts will require sacrifices as the
country is still generating deficits.  To contact the reporter on this story:
